605682000000.title: My First Note
605682000000.note:
The World Wide Web (*WWW*) is a global information medium which users can access via computers connected to the Internet. 

The term is often mistakenly used as a synonym for the Internet itself and often called *the Internet*, but the Web is a service that operates over the Internet.

The World Wide Web was invented by [Tim Berners-Lee](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tim_Berners-Lee) on March 12, 1989.
